description:
Decca
13.01.1938

Trusting my love
Foxtrot from "Sailing along"
(Johnston/Sigler)

Sidney Lipton and his Grosvenor House Orchestra
Vocal Chorus by Al Bowlly

Here's one of the two records that Al Bowlly recorded with Sidney Lipton. The tune - originally sung by Jessie Matthews - wasn't a big hit so the record wasn't a big seller. I hope you'll enjoy!
